#
# how to check if the network of a computer is locked
#
Phenomenon:
	ping didn't work
	rdp didn't work
	ex. can't ping file server from this computer.
	
Root cause:
	The computer's network is locked.
	And it falls out of domain.
	
Fix:
	call IT hotline.
	make sure the SCCM is green:
		McAfee is running ok (VirusScan Enterprise + AntiSpyware, McAfee Agent. )
		Windows update is running ok.
		...
	
